Sentencas: A series of A-site deficient Gd-containing Fe-Co-based cathodes were synthesized using the glycine-nitrate process.
Titulo: Studies of A-site Deficient (Gd0.6Sr0.4)1-sFe0.8Co0.2O3- Cathodes in SOFCs

Sentencas: All the compounds consisted of two phases, i.e., a cubic and orthorhombic phase, as determined by powder X-ray diffraction (XRD).
Titulo: Studies of A-site Deficient (Gd0.6Sr0.4)1-sFe0.8Co0.2O3- Cathodes in SOFCs

Sentencas: The thermal expansion coefficient decreased with increasing A-site deficiency, which could be because cobalt was expelled from the main phases.
Titulo: Studies of A-site Deficient (Gd0.6Sr0.4)1-sFe0.8Co0.2O3- Cathodes in SOFCs

Sentencas: Likewise, the electrochemical activities of the Gd-containing Fe-Co-based solid oxide fuel cell cathodes toward the reduction of oxygen ware improved by a factor of approximately 3 by making them A-site deficient.
Titulo: Studies of A-site Deficient (Gd0.6Sr0.4)1-sFe0.8Co0.2O3- Cathodes in SOFCs

Sentencas: The composition (Gd0.6Sr0.4)(0.85)Fe0.8Co0.2O3- showed the highest activity toward the reduction of oxygen among the five compounds.
Titulo: Studies of A-site Deficient (Gd0.6Sr0.4)1-sFe0.8Co0.2O3- Cathodes in SOFCs

Sentencas: Electrochemical impedance spectroscopy estimated the area specific resistance as 5.77 cm(2) at 600 degrees C.
Titulo: Studies of A-site Deficient (Gd0.6Sr0.4)1-sFe0.8Co0.2O3- Cathodes in SOFCs

Sentencas: The electrochemical impedance spectroscopy measurements revealed three arcs for most of the compounds at the three temperatures where the measurements were performed.
Titulo: Studies of A-site Deficient (Gd0.6Sr0.4)1-sFe0.8Co0.2O3- Cathodes in SOFCs
